 440	<!-- HOW TO PLAY MODAL -->
 441	<div id="howto-modal" style="display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(5,2,20,0.95);z-index:9999;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:1.5rem">
 442	  <div style="max-width:520px;width:100%;background:#12082a;border:1px solid #2a1a50;border-radius:12px;padding:1.8rem;overflow-y:auto;max-height:90vh">
 443	    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:1.2rem">
 444	      <div style="font-size:1.3rem;color:#c9b8ff;font-weight:700">🎸 How to Play</div>
 445	      <button onclick="document.getElementById('howto-modal').style.display='none'" style="background:none;border:1px solid #3a2a60;color:#6050a0;padding:0.3rem 0.8rem;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.9rem">✕</button>
 446	    </div>
 447	    <div style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#9080b0;line-height:1.8">
 448	      <div style="color:#c9b8ff;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem">🎯 Your Goal</div>
 449	      <p style="margin-bottom:1rem">You're a talent booker at a dive bar. Put on great shows each week, grow your reputation, and eventually upgrade your venue.</p>
 450	
 451	      <div style="color:#c9b8ff;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem">📅 The Week</div>
 452	      <p style="margin-bottom:0.5rem">Each week runs <strong style="color:#e0d0f8">Monday → Saturday</strong>. Press <em>Next Day →</em> to advance.</p>
 453	      <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin-bottom:1rem">
 454	        <li style="padding:0.3rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1028">📱 <strong style="color:#e0d0f8">BandBook</strong> — Browse acts and send enquiries. They reply within 1–2 days.</li>
 455	        <li style="padding:0.3rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1028">📬 <strong style="color:#e0d0f8">Inbox</strong> — When a band replies, their offer appears here with negotiation options.</li>
 456	        <li style="padding:0.3rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1028">🏠 <strong style="color:#e0d0f8">Office</strong> — See the week schedule and pick a mid-week promotion to boost attendance.</li>
 457	        <li style="padding:0.3rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1028">🎛️ <strong style="color:#e0d0f8">SFX Gear</strong> — Buy and activate production gear to enhance your shows.</li>
